{"word":"H5949 - עֲלִילָה - ʻălîylâh - al-ee-law' - Act","slug":"H5949","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עֲלִילָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻălîylâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>al-ee-law'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Act"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05DC;&#x05DC;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E2;&#x05DC;&#x05D9;&#x05DC;&#x05D4; - &#x201B;a&#x0306;l&#x0131;&#x0302;yla&#x0302;h  &#x201B;a&#x0306;lila&#x0302;h</b> - <i>al-ee-law', al-ee-law'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5953\">H5953</a> in the sense of <i>effecting</i>; an <i>exploit</i> (of God), or a <i>performance</i> (of man, often in a bad sense); by implication an <i>opportunity: - </i>act (-ion), deed, doing, invention, occasion, work."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4611\">H4611</a>, <a href=\"#/H5950\">H5950</a>, <a href=\"#/H5953\">H5953</a>, <a href=\"#/H5955\">H5955</a>, <a href=\"#/H8586\">H8586</a>"}]}